'''Loprana Soil-Enrichers''' was known to be a seedy company who had offices both in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] and the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. One of their known actions was stealing [[Ergesh]] technology from the [[Industrial Swampfields]].

